dataSource.name: Q_ANNEE_TRAITEE
dataSource.select: -- P_PARAM6 : Mois de traitement au format 'MMAAAA' -- (Si année est vide, prendre Année dans datdebex!!!) SELECT DECODE( SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 4, 4), NULL, TO_CHAR(datdebex, 'YYYY'), SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 4, 4) ) dc_annee_traitee FROM datdebex

dataSource.name: Q_PRODETA_ISAC
dataSource.select: -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- -- Query Etat $PRODETA (Ordre des colonnes est tel que ORDER BY est inutile) -- Détail des Consommés par Projet (pour une année) -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- SELECT DISTINCT bip.codsg dc_codsg, res.rnom dc_nomcp, bip.pid dc_pid, sst.ecet dc_num_etape, eta.typetap dc_typ_etap, sst.acta dc_num_tache, sst.acst dc_num_sstache, tac.aist dc_typ_sstache, tac.asnom dc_nom_sstache, decode(trim(pro.qualif),'GRA','NONFACT', 'MO','NONFACT', 'IFO','NONFACT', 'INT','NONFACT', 'STA','NONFACT', prest.CODE_DOMAINE) dc_codqualif_ress, decode(trim(pro.qualif),'GRA','NONFACT', 'MO','NONFACT', 'IFO','NONFACT', 'INT','NONFACT', 'STA','NONFACT', tdo.lib_domaine ) lib_domaine_ress, pro.rnom dc_nomres, str.sigdep dc_sigdep, str.sigpole dc_sigpole, str.codgro dc_codgro, bip.pnom dc_pnom, bip.pcpi dc_pcpi, bip.pcle dc_pcle, bip.ttrfbip dc_ttrfbip, sst.ident dc_ident, decode(trim(pro.qualif),'GRA',0, 'MO',0, 'IFO',0, 'INT',0, 'STA',0, 1) top_tri, DECODE( LEAST( '01', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '01', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('01', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) dc_conso_01, DECODE( LEAST( '02', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '02', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('02',SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) dc_conso_02, DECODE( LEAST( '03', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '03', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('03', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) dc_conso_03, DECODE( LEAST( '04', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '04', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('04',SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) dc_conso_04, DECODE( LEAST( '05', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '05', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('05', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) dc_conso_05, DECODE( LEAST( '06', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '06', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('06', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) dc_conso_06, DECODE( LEAST( '07', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '07', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('07', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) dc_conso_07, DECODE( LEAST( '08', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '08', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('08', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) dc_conso_08, DECODE( LEAST( '09', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '09', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('09', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) dc_conso_09, DECODE( LEAST( '10', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '10', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('10', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) dc_conso_10, DECODE( LEAST( '11', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '11', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('11',SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) dc_conso_11, DECODE( LEAST( '12', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '12', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('12',SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) dc_conso_12 FROM cons_sstache_res_mois sst, tache tac, proplus pro, etape eta, ligne_bip bip, ressource res, struct_info str, prestation prest, type_domaine tdo WHERE bip.pid = eta.pid AND eta.pid = tac.pid AND eta.ecet = tac.ecet AND tac.pid = sst.pid AND tac.ecet = sst.ecet AND tac.acta = sst.acta AND tac.acst = sst.acst AND bip.pid = pro.pid AND bip.codsg = pro.pdsg AND sst.ident = pro.tires AND sst.cdeb = pro.cdeb AND sst.ident != 0 AND bip.codsg = str.codsg (+) AND bip.pcpi = res.ident (+) and prest.PRESTATION = pro.qualif and tdo.CODE_DOMAINE = prest.CODE_DOMAINE &P_WHERE order by dc_codsg, dc_nomcp, dc_pid, dc_num_etape, dc_typ_etap, dc_num_tache, dc_num_sstache, dc_typ_sstache, dc_nom_sstache, top_tri, lib_domaine_ress, dc_nomres

dataSource.name: Q_TOTAL_DOMAINE_FACTU_PRJ
dataSource.select:
select ligne, domaine, sum(janv) janv, sum(fev) fev, sum(mars) mars, sum(avrl) avrl, sum(mai) mai, sum(juin) juin, sum(jui) jui, sum(aout) aout, sum(sept) sept, sum(oct) oct, sum(nov) nov, sum(dec) dec
from (
SELECT DISTINCT bip.pid ligne, tdo.lib_domaine domaine , DECODE( LEAST( '01', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '01', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('01', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) janv, DECODE( LEAST( '02', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '02', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('02',SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) fev, DECODE( LEAST( '03', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '03', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('03', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) mars, DECODE( LEAST( '04', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '04', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('04',SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) avrl, DECODE( LEAST( '05', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '05', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('05', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) mai, DECODE( LEAST( '06', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '06', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('06', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) juin, DECODE( LEAST( '07', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '07', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('07', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) jui, DECODE( LEAST( '08', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '08', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('08', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) aout, DECODE( LEAST( '09', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '09', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('09', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) sept, DECODE( LEAST( '10', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '10', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('10', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) oct, DECODE( LEAST( '11', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '11', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('11',SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) nov, DECODE( LEAST( '12', SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6, 1, 2) ), '12', pack_verif_prodeta.f_conso_ress_qualif('12',SUBSTR(:P_PARAM6 , 4, 4), bip.pid, sst.ecet, sst.acta, sst.acst, sst.ident,pro.qualif), 0 ) dec FROM cons_sstache_res_mois sst, tache tac, proplus pro, etape eta, ligne_bip bip, prestation prest, type_domaine tdo WHERE bip.pid = eta.pid AND eta.pid = tac.pid AND eta.ecet = tac.ecet AND tac.pid = sst.pid AND tac.ecet = sst.ecet AND tac.acta = sst.acta AND tac.acst = sst.acst AND bip.pid = pro.pid AND bip.codsg = pro.pdsg AND sst.ident = pro.tires AND sst.cdeb = pro.cdeb AND sst.ident != 0 and prest.PRESTATION = pro.qualif and tdo.CODE_DOMAINE = prest.CODE_DOMAINE -- on ne calcul pas ici les qualif non facturable c'est effectué dans le traitement principal and pro.qualif not in ('GRA','MO','IFO','INT','STA') &P_WHERE ) t1
group by ligne, domaine order by domaine
